Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.36,0:00:17.74,JoJo-main,lady,0000,0000,0000,,My, that looks so good on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.14,0:00:20.90,JoJo-main,lady,0000,0000,0000,,I've been working here for years,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.90,0:00:24.75,JoJo-main,lady,0000,0000,0000,,but I've never gotten such\N a strange request for clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.68,0:00:28.27,JoJo-main,jojo,0000,0000,0000,,I'm in a hurry. What's the total?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.34,0:00:30.27,JoJo-main,jojo,0000,0000,0000,,See ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.91,0:00:33.76,JoJo-main,lady,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Thank you...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.59,0:00:37.76,JoJo-main,anne,0000,0000,0000,,Let go! Let go of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.76,0:00:39.86,JoJo-main,anne,0000,0000,0000,,Don't touch me in weird places!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.86,0:00:41.27,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! Don't say it like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.09,0:00:41.27,JoJo-overlap,kakyo,0000,0000,0000,,Here's the ticket.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.27,0:00:42.80,JoJo-main,anne,0000,0000,0000,,No! I don't wanna!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.80,0:00:45.19,JoJo-main,anne,0000,0000,0000,,I want to go with you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.19,0:00:47.15,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Little Miss.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.15,0:00:52.69,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,My daughter, who is Jotaro's mother... \NHer life is in danger right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.06,0:00:58.70,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,We're going on this journey \Nto save my daughter's life.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.70,0:01:02.11,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Give up on running away and go back home.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.11,0:01:05.08,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure your parents are worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.82,0:01:06.81,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,There.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.81,0:01:11.41,JoJo-main,anne,0000,0000,0000,,Fine. I'll make you look good this time, Grandpa.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.09,0:01:16.53,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.01,0:01:19.01,JoJo-main,anne,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.55,0:01:24.10,JoJo-main,anne,0000,0000,0000,,See ya! Life is just a bunch of goodbyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.61,0:01:31.79,JoJo-internal/narrator,anne,0000,0000,0000,,But I did sort of want to see\N {\i0}him{\i1} again before I had to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.33,0:01:46.14,JoJo-main,anne,0000,0000,0000,,Bye-bye, Jojo! You better \Nsave your mom, no matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.14,0:01:49.01,JoJo-main,anne,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be cheering you on!
