Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.01,0:03:39.71,Jojo-Singapore,map,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,11618)}Karachi \N{\fs14} Indus River                          {\fs18}India
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.19,0:03:29.18,JoJo-topinternal,narration,0000,0000,0000,,Pakistan is a young country,\N established in 1947
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.18,0:03:32.77,JoJo-topinternal,narration,0000,0000,0000,,following its separation from India.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.77,0:03:36.67,JoJo-topinternal,narration,0000,0000,0000,,But when primitive peoples\N first began to live in Japan,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.67,0:03:39.10,JoJo-topinternal,narration,0000,0000,0000,,there was already civilization in Pakistan.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.84,0:03:43.41,JoJo-topinternal,narration,0000,0000,0000,,Here in Pakistan, the people \Ncarry on the five thousand year
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.41,0:03:45.81,JoJo-topinternal,narration,0000,0000,0000,,history of the Indian subcontinent.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.72,0:03:53.35,JoJo-EpTitle,ep title,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(675,660)}Episode 14: Justice Part 1
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.62,0:03:53.84,JoJo-top,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,But, Jotaro, I'm surprised you were \Nable to get someone to make you
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.84,0:03:56.40,JoJo-top,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,a Japanese school uniform here in Pakistan.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.27,0:04:02.19,JoJo-Location,derp,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(459,459)\b0\fs18}This story is fiction. The characters, groups, places, laws, and names \Nused in this program have no connection to any existing in real life.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.40,0:03:58.65,JoJo-top,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,The fit is perfect, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.65,0:04:00.66,JoJo-top,jojo,0000,0000,0000,,It's 100% wool.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.66,0:04:03.52,JoJo-top,kakyo,0000,0000,0000,,Polnareff, is it safe to drive right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.52,0:04:06.14,JoJo-main,kakyo,0000,0000,0000,,It appears the fog in this\N area is getting quite thick.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.14,0:04:09.39,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. It might be a bit dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.39,0:04:14.40,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,Since there's a sheer drop to \None side, and no guard rail.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.40,0:04:18.15,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed. The fog gets thicker up ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.95,0:04:22.57,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,It's not even 3:00 yet,\N but I guess we have no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.02,0:04:26.05,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Let's find a place to stay \Nin that town for the night.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.05,0:04:28.53,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if there's a nice hotel.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.53,0:04:30.23,JoJo-main,kakyo,0000,0000,0000,,A nice hotel?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.23,0:04:33.12,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,One that has a decent toilet, of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.12,0:04:36.25,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,I still can't get used to the \Ntoilets in India and West Asia
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.25,0:04:38.92,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,where you wash yourself with your hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.43,0:04:47.12,JoJo-internal/narrator,jojo,0000,0000,0000,,Was that a dog's corpse?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.55,0:04:49.43,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter, Jotaro?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.90,0:04:52.00,JoJo-main,jojo,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.86,0:05:01.86,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,This is a nice little town.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.67,0:05:05.75,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,I'd say it has a population of a few thousand.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.24,0:05:10.58,JoJo-main,kakyo,0000,0000,0000,,Let's ask about a hotel \Nat that restaurant there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.16,0:05:17.67,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,But it sure is a weirdly quiet town...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.67,0:05:22.43,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,Every other place has been \Nsuper crowded and noisy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.43,0:05:24.67,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,It's probably because of the fog.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.03,0:05:27.18,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Listen up, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.18,0:05:29.68,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,In Pakistan, and further\N west in the Islamic world,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.68,0:05:31.68,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,this is how you greet people.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.99,0:05:33.93,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,First, you smile and say...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.93,0:05:37.97,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Assalamu alaikum!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.98,0:05:58.83,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,E-Er... You didn't have to \Nclose up shop so suddenly...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.18,0:06:03.41,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,We just wanted to ask a question. \NIs there a hotel nearby?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.98,0:06:06.69,JoJo-Fwoom,sfx,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(551,450)}Silence
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.93,0:06:13.64,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.82,0:06:16.17,JoJo-main,guy,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.17,0:06:17.14,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.14,0:06:21.15,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wait a minute.\N What do you mean, you don't know?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.37,0:06:34.03,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What's with that guy...?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.52,0:06:36.04,JoJo-internal/narrator,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,I must have imagined it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.04,0:06:40.28,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure he couldn't understand you \Nbecause your pronunciation's so bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.28,0:06:42.54,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,Let's ask the guy sitting there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.07,0:06:46.63,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, guy! Sorry, but we're looking for a hotel.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.63,0:06:49.59,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,Preferably a hotel with nice, clean toilets.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.59,0:06:50.91,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know any...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.89,0:06:56.93,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! You!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.93,0:06:58.10,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.12,0:07:06.44,JoJo-main,three,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.44,0:07:11.95,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,They're dead! They died with \Nthat look of fear on their faces!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.95,0:07:15.70,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What the hell is this?\N Why are they lying dead in the road?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.03,0:07:17.29,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,What was the cause of death?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.29,0:07:20.46,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,A heart attack? A stroke?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.46,0:07:25.53,JoJo-main,jojo,0000,0000,0000,,That could be... But it doesn't \Nseem to be ordinary heart failure.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.63,0:07:31.84,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,A g-gun! This guy is holding a gun...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.84,0:07:33.59,JoJo-main,kakyo,0000,0000,0000,,You just noticed?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.91,0:07:36.14,JoJo-main,jojo,0000,0000,0000,,There's smoke coming from it. He's fired it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.14,0:07:40.37,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,And it was just fired.\N Maybe two to five minutes ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.15,0:07:45.47,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Either way, it was right \Nbefore we got to this town.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.11,0:07:48.53,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,Was it suicide? Did he shoot himself?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.53,0:07:51.91,JoJo-main,kakyo,0000,0000,0000,,No. There don't seem to \Nbe any wounds on the body,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.91,0:07:53.86,JoJo-main,kakyo,0000,0000,0000,,and there's no blood anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.86,0:07:56.87,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,Then how'd this guy die? Look at him!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.31,0:08:01.00,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,His face is distorted like he was \Nscreaming in utter terror!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.32,0:08:02.75,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.75,0:08:07.20,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,What did this man shoot with his gun?\N What in the world is going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.20,0:08:10.01,JoJo-main,kakyo,0000,0000,0000,,No one in the town noticed anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.41,0:08:12.26,JoJo-main,kakyo,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.26,0:08:15.17,JoJo-main,kakyo,0000,0000,0000,,Someone has died here. \NPlease call the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.67,0:08:33.36,JoJo-main,lady,0000,0000,0000,,Pardon. My acne seems to have festered.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.94,0:08:39.43,JoJo-main,lady,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, did you need something?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.67,0:08:43.37,JoJo-main,kakyo,0000,0000,0000,,I said I'd like you to call the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.37,0:08:45.00,JoJo-main,lady,0000,0000,0000,,The police?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.00,0:08:48.97,JoJo-main,lady,0000,0000,0000,,For what?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.97,0:08:52.05,JoJo-main,kakyo,0000,0000,0000,,Look! There's a dead body over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.47,0:08:59.36,JoJo-main,lady,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my. There's a dead body?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.98,0:09:02.93,JoJo-main,lady,0000,0000,0000,,Is there anything I can do?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.93,0:09:05.06,JoJo-main,kakyo,0000,0000,0000,,I already asked you to call the police!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.83,0:09:09.29,JoJo-main,lady,0000,0000,0000,,Right, right. Call the police...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.29,0:09:11.26,JoJo-main,lady,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.26,0:09:16.80,JoJo-main,lady,0000,0000,0000,,My acne has festered and \Nit's so itchy. Terribly itchy...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.31,0:09:23.62,JoJo-main,kakyo,0000,0000,0000,,What is with the people in this town?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.93,0:09:27.58,JoJo-main,kakyo,0000,0000,0000,,Someone died and not a\N single person even cares to look,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.58,0:09:29.24,JoJo-main,kakyo,0000,0000,0000,,let alone a whole curious crowd.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.46,0:09:34.34,JoJo-main,kakyo,0000,0000,0000,,Did they not even hear the gunshot?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.66,0:09:36.40,JoJo-main,kakyo,0000,0000,0000,,These people are even more indifferent
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.40,0:09:38.97,JoJo-main,kakyo,0000,0000,0000,,than people in large cities \Nlike New York or Tokyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.00,0:09:40.97,JoJo-internal/narrator,jojo,0000,0000,0000,,That dog...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.93,0:09:46.36,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,It feels like the fog just keeps getting thicker.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.36,0:09:49.49,JoJo-main,kakyo,0000,0000,0000,,The town seems to be engulfed by this fog.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.49,0:09:51.20,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,It's really creepy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.20,0:09:54.47,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't that part there look like a skull?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.70,0:10:12.03,JoJo-main,jojo,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want to do, old man?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.46,0:10:15.81,JoJo-main,jojo,0000,0000,0000,,You don't think it's the work \Nof another Stand user, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.65,0:10:17.73,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,It seems impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.73,0:10:18.76,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,There's no motive.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.29,0:10:21.38,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Would someone who's after us kill a man
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.38,0:10:24.63,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,who has nothing to do with us,\N before we even got here?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.63,0:10:27.09,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,If they did, why did they kill him?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.21,0:10:31.52,JoJo-main,jojo,0000,0000,0000,,But there is a possibility. \NHis death seems pretty extraordinary.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.32,0:10:33.66,JoJo-main,jojo,0000,0000,0000,,Let's investigate the body
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.66,0:10:36.30,JoJo-main,jojo,0000,0000,0000,,as much as we can without \Ntouching it, before the police come.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.30,0:10:37.28,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.78,0:10:43.78,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,It appears he was traveling, too, just like us.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.14,0:10:47.04,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,He has bus and train tickets.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.04,0:10:51.04,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,And he appears to be Indian. \NHe's carrying Indian money.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.04,0:10:53.41,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,He's not from this town.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.55,0:10:55.55,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.96,0:10:58.09,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,A wound!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.55,0:11:01.59,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Right under his throat, there's a wound \Nabout the size of a 10 yen coin.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.59,0:11:03.60,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Is this the cause of death?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.60,0:11:06.38,JoJo-main,jojo,0000,0000,0000,,But why isn't there any blood coming from it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.38,0:11:08.60,JoJo-main,jojo,0000,0000,0000,,With a hole this big, there should be
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.60,0:11:10.85,JoJo-main,jojo,0000,0000,0000,,tons of blood gushing from it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.85,0:11:12.45,JoJo-main,jojo,0000,0000,0000,,Normally, at least.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.39,0:11:17.21,JoJo-main,jojo,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like this is no ordinary murder.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.21,0:11:20.61,JoJo-main,jojo,0000,0000,0000,,We need to know. Let's not hold back.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.61,0:11:22.11,JoJo-main,jojo,0000,0000,0000,,Take off his clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.43,0:11:25.10,JoJo-Bam2,sfx,0000,0000,0000,,Bam
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.73,0:11:27.79,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What's with this corpse?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.79,0:11:30.29,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,There are holes all over it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.29,0:11:33.62,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,He looks like the cartoon cheese \Nyou'd see in {\i1}Tom & Jerry{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.62,0:11:37.05,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,And there's no blood coming \Nfrom any of these holes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.05,0:11:40.69,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,How on earth was this man killed?\N What does this all mean?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.69,0:11:42.05,JoJo-main,jojo,0000,0000,0000,,Be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.05,0:11:46.50,JoJo-main,jojo,0000,0000,0000,,The odds that there's a new \NStand user nearby just grew.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.65,0:11:49.53,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.53,0:11:51.64,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Get in the car! We're leaving this town!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.75,0:11:54.44,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.27,0:11:57.00,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,That's impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.00,0:11:58.69,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't the car!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.76,0:12:05.72,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Hermit Purple!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.40,0:12:15.66,JoJo-main,jojo,0000,0000,0000,,Hey. Old man.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.66,0:12:18.17,JoJo-main,jojo,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell are you doing?\N Are you stupid?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.44,0:12:21.94,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.94,0:12:25.37,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean, what am I doing?! \NThe car was right here a minute ago!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.37,0:12:26.65,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,What? Car?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.65,0:12:29.34,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,We just parked the car over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.34,0:12:30.43,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.43,0:12:33.36,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,B-But just now...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.62,0:12:54.51,JoJo-main,enya,0000,0000,0000,,You seem to be travelers.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.51,0:12:59.10,JoJo-main,enya,0000,0000,0000,,With this fog, it's dangerous \Nto leave the town now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.10,0:13:01.51,JoJo-main,enya,0000,0000,0000,,There are many cliffs, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.51,0:13:05.08,JoJo-main,enya,0000,0000,0000,,I run a little bed and breakfast.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.08,0:13:09.85,JoJo-main,enya,0000,0000,0000,,If you'd like, why not stay there for the night?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.85,0:13:12.82,JoJo-main,enya,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make it cheap.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.82,0:13:15.79,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,We finally met a normal person!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.25,0:13:23.94,JoJo-Eyecatch3,signtop,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(801,1)}Hermit Purple
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.96,0:13:23.94,JoJo-Eyecatch2,signbot,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(967,1)}Joseph Joestar
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.07,0:13:27.95,JoJo-main,kakyo,0000,0000,0000,,There's a strong possibility that
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.95,0:13:30.69,JoJo-main,kakyo,0000,0000,0000,,a Stand user is hiding somewhere in this town.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.69,0:13:34.70,JoJo-main,kakyo,0000,0000,0000,,This thick fog also gives them the upper hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.70,0:13:37.96,JoJo-main,kakyo,0000,0000,0000,,We cannot let our guard down at all tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.96,0:13:43.33,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,But... even without anyone attacking us,\Nthis is a really creepy town.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.12,0:13:50.35,JoJo-main,enya,0000,0000,0000,,Come now, Mr. Joestar. That is my hotel.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.35,0:13:55.07,JoJo-main,enya,0000,0000,0000,,I shall lead the way. Please come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.73,0:13:59.72,JoJo-main,enya,0000,0000,0000,,This hotel is small...\N but about twenty years ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.72,0:14:03.14,JoJo-main,enya,0000,0000,0000,,one of the 007 films was filmed here,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.14,0:14:08.99,JoJo-main,enya,0000,0000,0000,,and John Lennon from the \NBeatles even stayed here once.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.99,0:14:10.62,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,What? Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.62,0:14:13.24,JoJo-main,enya,0000,0000,0000,,No, not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.24,0:14:13.95,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,Wha?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.95,0:14:18.74,JoJo-main,enya,0000,0000,0000,,But it is still quite a nice hotel.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.74,0:14:21.99,JoJo-main,enya,0000,0000,0000,,There are currently no other guests.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.99,0:14:24.72,JoJo-main,enya,0000,0000,0000,,Would meat for dinner be all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.72,0:14:27.39,JoJo-main,enya,0000,0000,0000,,Or would you prefer fish?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.95,0:14:27.39,JoJo-overlap,jojo,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it, old lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.96,0:14:30.89,JoJo-main,jojo,0000,0000,0000,,You just said "Joestar," didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.81,0:14:34.64,JoJo-main,jojo,0000,0000,0000,,How'd you know that name?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.32,0:14:53.23,JoJo-main,enya,0000,0000,0000,,Come now, sir. That person there\N just said "Mr. Joestar" a moment ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.23,0:14:54.81,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,What? Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.81,0:14:56.83,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I guess I might have.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.83,0:14:58.90,JoJo-main,enya,0000,0000,0000,,You did, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.90,0:15:02.32,JoJo-main,enya,0000,0000,0000,,When you've been in customer \Nservice for many years,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.32,0:15:05.34,JoJo-main,enya,0000,0000,0000,,you learn to memorize \Npeople's names quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.71,0:15:08.09,JoJo-main,enya,0000,0000,0000,,So I'm sure of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.42,0:15:12.36,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, Ma'am,\N what happened to your left hand?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.36,0:15:16.19,JoJo-main,enya,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, this? I just burned it a little...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.19,0:15:18.11,JoJo-main,enya,0000,0000,0000,,It might because of my old age,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.11,0:15:21.69,JoJo-main,enya,0000,0000,0000,,but I accidentally spilled boiling water on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.69,0:15:24.21,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,Age? What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.21,0:15:26.77,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,You only look to be about forty.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.77,0:15:28.95,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I'll ask you on a date.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.13,0:15:34.19,JoJo-main,enya,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't tease me so, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.32,0:15:40.41,JoJo-internal/narrator,enya,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell are you saying, you fool?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.41,0:15:43.52,JoJo-internal/narrator,enya,0000,0000,0000,,I hate you most of all, Polnareff!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.52,0:15:46.62,JoJo-internal/narrator,enya,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make sure you suffer a\N thousand times what my son did
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.62,0:15:52.72,JoJo-internal/narrator,enya,0000,0000,0000,,when I cut your dick off and\N rip out your guts to kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.07,0:15:57.76,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, this doesn't look too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.82,0:16:00.40,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,Here, Kakyoin.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.40,0:16:01.28,JoJo-main,kakyo,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.15,0:16:05.04,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,My autograph's worth as much as Lennon's.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.32,0:16:05.04,JoJo-overlap,kakyo,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.04,0:16:06.12,JoJo-overlap,jojo,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.04,0:16:06.90,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,I'm {\i1}Paul{\i0}nareff, after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.34,0:16:09.16,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,Make sure you take care of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.16,0:16:10.65,JoJo-main,enya,0000,0000,0000,,My, my...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.04,0:16:13.53,JoJo-main,enya,0000,0000,0000,,I will do just that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.00,0:16:17.03,JoJo-internal/narrator,enya,0000,0000,0000,,To commemorate your death!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.03,0:16:18.24,JoJo-main,jojo,0000,0000,0000,,It's done.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.24,0:16:22.79,JoJo-main,enya,0000,0000,0000,,Well, then... I will show you to your rooms.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.51,0:16:33.87,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,Man... Talk about a weird town.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.35,0:16:39.01,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,All right, I'm going to the bathroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.71,0:16:43.76,JoJo-main,kakyo,0000,0000,0000,,It appears to be broken.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.42,0:16:47.04,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Then I won't be able to use Hermit Purple to
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.04,0:16:48.46,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,get information on the enemy...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.46,0:16:50.19,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Mr. Joestar.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.19,0:16:51.39,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.39,0:16:52.85,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,Is there a bathroom in this room?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.85,0:16:55.12,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,There doesn't seem to be one in mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.12,0:16:57.70,JoJo-main,kakyo,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe the bathroom here is communal.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.70,0:16:59.45,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.63,0:17:03.61,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Good grief. He's so carefree.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.61,0:17:08.35,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,An unknown Stand user\N could attack at any moment...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.23,0:17:31.07,JoJo-main,hol,0000,0000,0000,,So, the Joestar party is on the third floor?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.93,0:17:35.57,JoJo-main,enya,0000,0000,0000,,Hol Horse... So, you've come.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.57,0:17:40.62,JoJo-main,hol,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. I just now tracked them as far as this town.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.62,0:17:43.50,JoJo-main,hol,0000,0000,0000,,But you surprised me, Enyaba.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.50,0:17:46.12,JoJo-main,hol,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't think you'd come here yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.39,0:18:01.10,JoJo-main,hol,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What's wrong, Enyaba?\N You just started crying out of nowhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.30,0:18:07.73,JoJo-main,enya,0000,0000,0000,,I-I am happy, Hol Horse!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.73,0:18:09.34,JoJo-main,enya,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.34,0:18:13.79,JoJo-main,enya,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for coming to see \Nthis lonely old woman!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.79,0:18:18.36,JoJo-main,enya,0000,0000,0000,,I am very happy to see you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.88,0:18:26.62,JoJo-main,enya,0000,0000,0000,,Hol Horse, you were my \Nson's friend, were you not?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.62,0:18:28.00,JoJo-main,hol,0000,0000,0000,,Friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.00,0:18:29.25,JoJo-main,hol,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Wha...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.25,0:18:30.65,JoJo-main,hol,0000,0000,0000,,A-Ahem...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.65,0:18:32.63,JoJo-main,hol,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I certainly was.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.63,0:18:35.88,JoJo-main,enya,0000,0000,0000,,Sob, sob. Were you close?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.88,0:18:37.51,JoJo-main,hol,0000,0000,0000,,Close?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.51,0:18:39.38,JoJo-main,hol,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! He was a dear friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.38,0:18:41.26,JoJo-main,hol,0000,0000,0000,,We were an excellent team.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.26,0:18:45.01,JoJo-main,hol,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong? This isn't like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.74,0:18:53.36,JoJo-main,enya,0000,0000,0000,,Will you avenge my son?\N Is that why you've come?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.36,0:18:55.73,JoJo-main,hol,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! That's exactly it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.73,0:18:59.11,JoJo-main,hol,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to avenge my best friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.19,0:19:06.16,JoJo-main,enya,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I'm so happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.87,0:19:03.59,JoJo-Swoop,sfx,0000,0000,0000,,Swoop
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.35,0:19:06.16,JoJo-Swoop,sfx,0000,0000,0000,,Stab
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.41,0:19:12.75,JoJo-main,enya,0000,0000,0000,,Because I can kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.34,0:19:18.13,JoJo-main,hol,0000,0000,0000,,E-Enyaba?! Wh-What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.72,0:19:29.26,JoJo-main,enya,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you abandon my son \Nto save yourself, Hol Horse?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.26,0:19:33.79,JoJo-main,enya,0000,0000,0000,,I was determined to kill you \Nas soon as I saw you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.79,0:19:37.90,JoJo-main,enya,0000,0000,0000,,My son's best friend? How dare you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.90,0:19:39.82,JoJo-main,hol,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wait! You've got it all wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.82,0:19:43.48,JoJo-main,hol,0000,0000,0000,,When I got there,\NCenterfold was already dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.45,0:19:51.13,JoJo-main,enya,0000,0000,0000,,Unforgivable! You are as \Nunforgivable as Polnareff!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.13,0:19:54.63,JoJo-main,enya,0000,0000,0000,,I'll have you die by the\N hands of my Stand, Justice!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.95,0:19:56.63,JoJo-main,hol,0000,0000,0000,,J-Justice?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.16,0:20:07.11,JoJo-main,enya,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure you've heard of it, \Nbut haven't seen it yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.11,0:20:11.10,JoJo-main,enya,0000,0000,0000,,I shall show you now, Hol Horse!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.36,0:20:18.76,JoJo-main,hol,0000,0000,0000,,Th-The blood from my arm \Nwhere the scissors stabbed it...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.76,0:20:21.07,JoJo-main,hol,0000,0000,0000,,It's going up into the fog...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.13,0:20:23.86,JoJo-Swoop,sfx,0000,0000,0000,,Splort
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.82,0:20:30.04,JoJo-main,enya,0000,0000,0000,,A fine hole has appeared!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.04,0:20:34.39,JoJo-main,enya,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. My Stand, Justice, \Nis a Stand made of fog.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.39,0:20:40.08,JoJo-main,enya,0000,0000,0000,,Any wound touched by this fog \Nbecomes a fine hole like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.08,0:20:41.55,JoJo-main,enya,0000,0000,0000,,And then...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.51,0:20:48.01,JoJo-main,enya,0000,0000,0000,,Justice wants to dance!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.76,0:20:54.32,JoJo-main,enya,0000,0000,0000,,The fog has entered the\N hole in your arm, like a string!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.32,0:20:56.78,JoJo-main,enya,0000,0000,0000,,And now, you are my puppet!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.78,0:21:01.69,JoJo-main,enya,0000,0000,0000,,Die by your own hand, Hol Horse!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.38,0:21:01.80,JoJo-Snap,sfx,0000,0000,0000,,Smash
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.82,0:21:12.04,JoJo-main,hol,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it! Don't get so cocky!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.04,0:21:13.45,JoJo-main,hol,0000,0000,0000,,Emperor!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.99,0:21:16.21,JoJo-main,hol,0000,0000,0000,,Die, you shitty old hag!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.88,0:21:23.21,JoJo-main,enya,0000,0000,0000,,Justice will triumph!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.64,0:21:28.72,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,What was that noise?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.19,0:21:32.05,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,That room at the back of \Nthe lobby is really loud...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.23,0:21:40.43,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Is something wrong, Polnareff?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.90,0:21:44.36,JoJo-main,kakyo,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I heard a strange noise.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.36,0:21:47.07,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to take a look downstairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.07,0:21:51.08,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be in the lobby,\N so call me if you need me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.55,0:22:03.97,JoJo-main,enya,0000,0000,0000,,Curse you, Polnareff!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.97,0:23:37.01,JoJo-Preview,sign,0000,0000,0000,,Next Episode Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.54,0:23:39.14,JoJo-main,enya,0000,0000,0000,,I just saw him. He's in the bathroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.14,0:23:40.52,JoJo-main,jojo,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, the bathroom?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.92,0:23:43.00,JoJo-main,enya,0000,0000,0000,,The bathroom is just past that door.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.00,0:23:46.54,JoJo-main,kakyo,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I just heard someone say "toilet."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.54,0:23:49.99,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,I always seem to get attacked in bathrooms...
